00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:48.490
There are other colours of noise, too, corresponding
to different frequencies like how coloured

00:02:48.490 --> 00:02:50.290
light focuses on different wavelengths.

00:02:50.290 --> 00:02:55.190
There’s red or brown noise, blue noise,
violet, black, green, and orange noise, though

