00:02:58.580 --> 00:03:00.270
So why do we find white noise soothing?

00:03:00.270 --> 00:03:02.660
Well, it’s a personal preference thing.

00:03:02.660 --> 00:03:06.310
Some people love white noise and some hate
it, but most people find it helpful for sleep

00:03:06.310 --> 00:03:09.310
because of it’s ability to mask other sounds.

00:03:09.310 --> 00:03:12.270
And really, don’t we all want a nice, quiet
night’s sleep?

